    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Games that require players to solve or navigate a challenge to progress to another more difficult challenge. These are usually single-player games, but may involve multiple players depending on the game type.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
